-Your a level 45 shadow knight. You weild a wurmslayer and a shield or whatever. Your grouped with another level 45 shadow knight. He weilds the exact same thing you do. He hits for the exact same amount as you, at the same time too. The mob won't aggro him, it will aggro you because of the mask. -<BR>
